title: Sensors Are Placed
text: While you control more Hoth objectives than your opponent, that opponent must place his first card in each edge battle faceup.

title: Echo Defender
text: This unit gains [Edge-Enabled Unit Damage] for each Hoth objective you control.

title: Echo Defender
text: This unit gains [Edge-Enabled Unit Damage] for each Hoth objective you control.

title: Echo Base
text:
Enhance your play area.
Each of your Hoth objectives gains +1 damage capacity.
You are considered to control 1 additional Hoth objective.

title: Echo Base Shield Generator
text:
Enhance your play area.
Action: Place 1 damage on this enhancement to place 1 shield on a target unit or Hoth objective. Then, if this enhancement has 3 or more damage on it, return it to your hand. (Limit once per turn.)

title: First Marker
text:
Enhance a Hoth objective.
Enhanced objective cannot be damaged by Vehicle units.

title: Renegade Squadron Mobilization
text: Reaction: After an enemy unit leaves play, draw 1 card.

title: Renegade Squadron
text:
Elite. (Remove 1 additional focus token from this unit when you refresh.)
Reaction: After this unit is focused to strike as an attacker, damage it to rescue 1 card captured at the engaged objective.

keywords.text: Remove 1 additional focus token from this unit when you refresh.

title: Munitions Expert
text: Action: Focus this unit to have a target unit gain [Unit Damage] until the end of the phase.

title: Echo Caverns
text:
Enhance your play area.
Action: Focus this enhancement to target 2 units that share a Trait. Until the end of the phase, one of those units loses a combat icon of your choice, and the other gains that combat icon.

title: Target of Opportunity
text: If you are the attacking player, deal 1 damage to the engaged objective.

title: Preparation for Battle
text:
Your shielded units cannot be damaged while the Death Star dial is 4 or lower.
Your shielded units gain [Blast Damage] while the Death Star dial is 8 or higher.

title: Hoth Scout
text: Action: Sacrifice this unit to place 1 shield on a target unit or objective.

title: AAC-1 Speeder Tank
text: Shielding. (When this unit enters an engagement, place 1 shield on any unit or objective in the engagement.)

title: Shelter from the Storm
text:
Play only if there is a Hoth objective in play.
Action: Place 1 shield on a target friendly Character unit. Until the end of the phase, that unit cannot be targeted by enemy card effects and cannot be damaged.

title: Deploy the Fleet
text: Action: Damage this objective to reduce the cost of the next Capital Ship unit you play this phase by 1.

title: Death Squadron Star Destroyer
text:
Shielding. (When this unit enters an engagement, place 1 shield on any unit or objective in the engagement.)
This unit cannot be targeted by enemy events.

title: Death Squadron Command
text:
Enhance your play area.
Reaction: After an objective is destroyed, remove 1 focus token from this enhancement.

title: Admiral's Orders
text: Action: Reduce the cost of the next Capital Ship unit you play this phase by 2.

title: Jabba's Orders
text: Reaction: After this objective enters play, look at an opponent's hand.

title: Weequay Elite
text: Reduce the cost to play this unit by 2 if there is at least 1 card captured at any of your objectives.

title: Jawa Trading Crawler
text: Resources generated by this unit can only be used to play Vehicle or Droid units.

title: Jabba's Palace
text:
Enhance your play area.
Each of your objectives gains +1 damage capacity.

title: Get Me Solo!
text:
Play only during your turn.
Action: Name a unit, then reveal an opponent's hand. Capture all copies of the named unit in that hand.
